    "attributes": {
        "action": "Add Vehicle Trades (523) occupations to Shortage Occupations List",
        "additional_details": "Adding these occupations should help alleviate employment shortages in this sector, making it easier for businesses to recruit skilled and qualified foreign workers.\r\n \r\nMany workshops and bodyshops are, or have, experienced difficulties when recruiting and retaining staff. Leading to:\r\n \r\n\u2022 Lost income\r\n\u2022 Increased staff costs & labour costs to customers\r\n\u2022 More transient staff\r\n\u2022 Employing less competent staff",
        "background": "There's a severe shortage of motor vehicle workers in the UK, affecting businesses, customers and the economy.\r\n \r\nWe need motor industry Technicians, Painters and Panel Beaters on the Shortage Occupations List.\r\n \r\nThis would make it easier for employers to recruit qualified/skilled staff.",
